@startuml
title State machine model of a digital watch

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
Idle : display time
Idle : display alarm status

state Adjusting
Adjusting : increase hour value
Adjusting : increase minute value
Adjusting : increase alarm hour value
Adjusting : increase alarm minute value

state Alarm
Alarm : display alarm status
Alarm : trigger alarm

state Stopped
Stopped : display stopped alarm status

state LightOn
LightOn : display light status

state LightOff
LightOff : display light status

Idle --> Adjusting : Button Pressed
Adjusting --> Idle : Button Released
Adjusting --> Alarm : Alarm Button Pressed
Alarm --> Stopped : Alarm Time Matched
Stopped --> Alarm : Alarm Button Pressed
Alarm --> LightOn : Light Button Pressed
LightOn --> LightOff : Light Button Released
LightOff --> LightOn : Light Button Pressed
Idle --> LightOn : Light Button Pressed
LightOff --> Idle : Light Button Released

@enduml
